                            <comment id="354225" author="laisiyao" created="Sat, 26 Nov 2022 03:25:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The failure in replay-single 111g is lod_trans_space_check()&lt;del&gt;&amp;gt;dt_statfs()&lt;/del&gt;&amp;gt;osp_statfs() returns -ENOTCONN during replay. I&apos;ll push a patch to make lod_trans_space_check() fail in low space only, but skip other failures which will be detected in operation processing.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
